{
  "id": 5200068565139456,
  "name": "Lazy loading for video and audio elements",
  "summary": "Adds the loading attribute to <video> and <audio> elements, allowing developers to defer media resource loading until the element is near the viewport using loading=\"lazy\". This matches the existing lazy loading behavior for <img> and <iframe>\n elements, improving page load performance and reducing data usage.\n\n\nCL: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/7511253\n\n\n",
